stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Uninitialized: Project created
    Uninitialized --> Scaffolded: foundryspec init
    Scaffolded --> Building: foundryspec build
    Building --> Ready: dist/ generated
    Ready --> Serving: foundryspec serve
    Ready --> Deploying: foundryspec deploy
    Deploying --> Ready
    Serving --> Ready: Stop server
    
    Scaffolded --> Upgrading: foundryspec upgrade
    Upgrading --> Scaffolded
